  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The Evil Boxes Are Back!!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261420/extras/c89c4060d34ce501f02e38715a9b200f.poster.avif?t=1771608303\" width=381 height=209 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261420/extras/c89c4060d34ce501f02e38715a9b200f.webm?t=1771608303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decipher The Riddles Given To You By Dad and Stomp The Right box Color; To Advance Through The Game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every Level Has a Unique Design That Corresponds With The Riddle You Are Given. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Solve The Mystery of The Time Looping Evil Boxes and Save Our Hero Aous In His Puzzling Adventure.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261420/extras/bcfcf6677693751a16ec8a923f4b7d55.poster.avif?t=1771608303\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261420/extras/bcfcf6677693751a16ec8a923f4b7d55.webm?t=1771608303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261420/extras/bcfcf6677693751a16ec8a923f4b7d55.mp4?t=1771608303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Riddles Have To Be Solved Relatively Fast or The Evil Box Will Cause The Time To Loop Again.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The Evil Boxes Are Back!!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261420/extras/c89c4060d34ce501f02e38715a9b200f.poster.avif?t=1771608303\" width=381 height=209 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261420/extras/c89c4060d34ce501f02e38715a9b200f.webm?t=1771608303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decipher The Riddles Given To You By Dad and Stomp The Right box Color; To Advance Through The Game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every Level Has a Unique Design That Corresponds With The Riddle You Are Given. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Solve The Mystery of The Time Looping Evil Boxes and Save Our Hero Aous In His Puzzling Adventure.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261420/extras/bcfcf6677693751a16ec8a923f4b7d55.poster.avif?t=1771608303\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261420/extras/bcfcf6677693751a16ec8a923f4b7d55.webm?t=1771608303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261420/extras/bcfcf6677693751a16ec8a923f4b7d55.mp4?t=1771608303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Riddles Have To Be Solved Relatively Fast or The Evil Box Will Cause The Time To Loop Again.</p>",
